'''Ralph Smith''' is a Paralympic swimming competitor from Australia.  He won a bronze medal at the [[1988 Summer Paralympics|1988 Seoul Games]] in the Men's 100 m Freestyle A7 event.<ref name=IPC-AUS>{{cite web|title=Athlete Search Results|url=http://www.paralympic.org/Sport/Results/search.html?npc=AUS&gender=all&medal=medals&sport=all&games=1992PG|publisher=International Paralympic Committee|accessdate=30 September 2011}}</ref>

